<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.10">
<l>yāvaiyum yavarun tāṉā yavaravar camayan tōṟun</l>
<l>tōyvilaṉ pulaṉain tukkuñ colappaṭā ṉuṇarviṉ mūrtti</l>
<l>yāvicē ruyiri ṉuḷḷā lātumōr paṟṟi lāta</l>
<l>pāvaṉai yataṉaik kūṭi lavaṉaiyuṅ kūṭa lāmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being everything and everyone, all those people in all the creeds,</l>
<l>the one without touch, the one not spoken about when shedding the five senses, the form of perception,</l>
<l>the imagination that exists without any support of all that by the inside of the breath</l>
<l>that joins the soul, if you join that, it is possible to join with him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
